data.description: Welcome to this Charming, Cozy home located in the Convenient and Desirable Loma Linda Subdivision.Featuring a landscaped front yard, real grass and a privacy fence in the backyard. Windows and doors have security wrought iron. Inside, the home features an open kitchen, Granite countertops, two full baths, three good sized bedrooms, ceiling fans and a garage with storage space complete with garage door opener. Don't miss out on this great Home and Great neighborhood! Please verify all Schools. Home is occupied.*Oven does not convey
